 2009-08732009-06-04,  ,  ,  ,  AGRI-FOOD, 
ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgri-Recovery - Quebec Nematode Assistance Program
PrecisOrder providing for additional financial assistance through the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program under the AgriRecovery Framework to potato and nursery farms affected by golden nematode in Quebec through a contribution under the federal component of the 2009 Quebec Nematode Assistance Program.
